{
  "stem": "4570.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And again, we, we didn't make any arrangements, because I was again to get word through somebody where to meet, because they didn't know if the Czech families could have been already evacuated.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because slowly, slowly, they were moving all, all the the non-Jewish people out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I went back home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I went to the mother, and I told her that I have seen Goldie, that everything is fine.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And about two days later, a, a Czech girl came to me, and my Czech was so poor.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I knew it was something terribly bad she's, she's telling me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And eventually, I worked it out with her that he had a cart.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he had an after- hour pass, which I don't know what they had it for-- maybe if somebody died that they, they carried the bodies at night.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Anyhow, when I left all the luggage there, he put it in his little cart.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he had his after-hour pass.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And off he went to where he was living.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And a Czech gendarme or sort of a country policemen-- a Czech, mind you-- caught him and put him in with the German authorities.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Then all I know, what I've been told, he went to the small fortress.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He was-- that was terrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They beat them there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They tortured them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And knowing that, that my visit caused all this disaster-- I mean, sure, it wasn't my idea.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But it was his idea, but I cooperated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And my cooperation caused all this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I just was frantic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And there was no way of, of getting any, any-- even if people went to the ghetto, they still didn't know what's going on in, in the fortress.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
